{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/settargetcoordinate:animated:completionhandler:"]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setTargetCoordinate:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@CLLocationCoordinate2D","text":"CLLocationCoordinate2D","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"targetCoordinate","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"animated:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL","text":"BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"animated","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"completionHandler:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" (^)()) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"completion","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The target coordinate to fit within the viewport.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"targetCoordinate"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If ","type":"text"},{"code":"YES","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", the map animates to fit the target within the map","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"view. If ","type":"text"},{"code":"NO","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", the map fits the target instantaneously.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"animated"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The block executed after the animation finishes.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"completion"}]},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"By default, the target coordinate is set to an invalid coordinate, indicating","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"that there is no target. In course tracking mode, the target forms one of two","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"foci in the viewport, the other being the user location annotation. Typically,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the target is set to a destination or waypoint in a real-time navigation scene.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"As the user annotation moves toward the target, the map automatically zooms in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to fit both foci optimally within the viewport.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"This method has no effect if the ","type":"text"},{"code":"userTrackingMode","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" property is set to a value","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"other than ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserTrackingMode\/MLNUserTrackingModeFollowWithCourse","type":"reference"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"metadata":{"symbolKind":"method","remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNMapView.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L799"},"title":"setTargetCoordinate:animated:completionHandler:","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setTargetCoordinate:animated:completionHandler:"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setTargetCoordinate:animated:completionHandler:","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"role":"symbol","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(im)setTargetCoordina